\c 8
\nb
\v 1 Kungathi ngabe unjengomfowethu owamunya amabele kamama! \add Uba\add* bengingakufica phandle, bengingakwanga, yebo, bebengayikungidelela.
\v 2 Bengingakukhokhela ngikungenise endlini kamama, ubengangifundisa\x + 3.4.\x*; bengingakunathisa okwewayini elilesinongo\x + Zaga 9.2,5.\x*, okomhluzi\x + Isa. 49.26.\x* wepomegranati lami\x + 4.3.\x*.
\v 3 Isandla sakhe sokhohlo singaphansi kwekhanda lami\x + 2.6.\x*, lesokunene saso siyangigona\x + 2.6.\x*.
\v 4 Ngiyalifungisa\x + 2.7.\x*, lina madodakazi eJerusalema, ukuze lingaphazamisi lingavusi uthando aze athande\x + 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Ngubani lo owenyuka evela enkangala eyeme kothandekayo wakhe\x + 3.6.\x*? Ngakuvusa ngaphansi\x + 8.4.\x* kwesihlahla sama-aphula\x + Zaga 25.11.\x*, kulapho unyoko akuhelela khona, kulapho ahelelwa khona owakuzalayo.
\p
\v 6 Ngibeka njengophawu enhliziyweni yakho, njengophawu engalweni yakho\x + Jer. 22.24. Isa. 49.16. 2 Tim. 2.19.\x*; ngoba uthando lulamandla njengokufa\x + Roma 8.35.\x*, ubukhwele bulesihluku njengengcwaba\x + Zaga 6.34,35.\x*; amalahle alo angamalahle omlilo\x + Jobe 5.7. Hlab. 78.48.\x*, ilangabi\x + Jobe 15.30. Hez. 20.47.\x* elilamandla kakhulu\x + Jobe 1.16. Hlab. 68.4.\x*.
\v 7 Amanzi amanengi kawalakulucitsha uthando, lezimpophoma kazilugalulisi. Uba umuntu ubenganika impahla yonke yendlu yakhe ngothando, bebengayidelela lokuyidelela\x + 8.4.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Silodadewethu omncinyane, njalo kalamabele\x + Hez. 16.7.\x*. Sizamenzelani udadewethu ngosuku mhla kukhulunywa ngaye?
\v 9 Uba engumduli, sizakwakha phezu kwakhe inqaba yesiliva\x + Hlab. 69.25.\x*, njalo uba engumnyango, sizamvalela ngamapulanka omsedari\x + 1 Kho. 6.15.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ngingumduli, lamabele ami anjengemiphotshongo\x + 5.13. 4.5.\x*; khona emehlweni akhe ngaba njengokufumene umusa\f + \fk umusa: \fl Heb. \fq ukuthula.\f*.
\v 11 USolomoni wayelesivini\x + Tshu. 2.4.\x* eBhali-Hamoni, wanikela isivini\x + Mat. 21.33. Hlab. 80.8.\x* kubalindi\x + 1.6.\x*; ngulowo lalowo wayezaletha ngezithelo zaso inhlamvu zesiliva eziyinkulungwane\x + Isa. 7.23.\x*.
\v 12 Isivini sami esingesami siphambi kwami; \add inhlamvu\add* eziyinkulungwane ngezakho, Solomoni\x + Isa. 7.23.\x*, lamakhulu amabili\x + 1 Kor. 3.8,9. 9.7.\x* ngawabalindi bezithelo zaso\x + 1.6.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Wena ohlala ezivandeni\x + 5.1.\x*, abangane balalela ilizwi lakho\x + 1.7. Jobe 41.6.\x*; ngizwise lona\x + 2.14.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Phangisa, sithandwa sami\x + Isam. 22.17,20. Hlab. 55.6.\x*, ube njengomziki kumbe njengethole lendluzele phezu kwezintaba zamakha\x + 2.9,17.\x*.
